TITLE: Initializing CometChat SDK in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to initialize the CometChat SDK with your app ID. It includes the initialization parameters and handling of the response through a Promise.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cometchat/chat-sdk-react-native/blob/v4/LICENSE.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const appID = "APP_ID";
const region = "REGION";
const appSetting = new CometChat.AppSettings({
  subscriptionType: CometChat.SubscriptionType.ALL_USERS,
});

CometChat.init(appID, appSetting, region).then(
  () => {
    console.log("Initialization completed successfully");
    // You can now proceed with rendering your app or calling login function.
  },
  (error) => {
    console.log("Initialization failed with error:", error);
    // Check the reason for error and take appropriate action.
  }
);
```

