TITLE: Importing CometChat SDK in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to import the CometChat SDK in a React Native application. It demonstrates importing both the core SDK and UI components required for implementing chat functionality.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cometchat/chat-sdk-react-native/blob/v4/LICENSE.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { CometChat } from "@cometchat/chat-sdk-react-native";
import { CometChatUIKit } from "@cometchat/chat-uikit-react-native";
```

