TITLE: User Login with CometChat SDK in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to log in a user to CometChat using their UID and API key. It demonstrates handling the login response through a Promise pattern.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cometchat/chat-sdk-react-native/blob/v4/LICENSE.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const authKey = "AUTH_KEY";
const uid = "UID";

CometChat.login(uid, authKey).then(
  (user) => {
    console.log("Login Successful:", { user });
  },
  (error) => {
    console.log("Login failed with exception:", { error });
  }
);
```

