TITLE: Initializing CometChat UIKit in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to initialize the CometChat UIKit, which provides ready-to-use UI components for chat functionality. It includes setting up the UIKit with the required parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cometchat/chat-sdk-react-native/blob/v4/LICENSE.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const uiKitSettings = new CometChatUIKit.UIKitSettings({
  // Add UIKit settings here
});

CometChatUIKit.init({
  appId: appID,
  authKey: authKey,
  region: region,
  extensions: {},
  uiKitSettings,
}).then(() => {
  // UIKit initialization successful
});
```

