TITLE: Creating a Chat UI Component in React Native with CometChat
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a chat UI component using CometChat's UIKit in a React Native application. It shows a functional component that renders a complete chat interface.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cometchat/chat-sdk-react-native/blob/v4/LICENSE.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import React from 'react';
import { CometChatConversationsWithMessages } from '@cometchat/chat-uikit-react-native';

const ChatsScreen = () => {
  return (
    <CometChatConversationsWithMessages />
  );
};

export default ChatsScreen;
```

